OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUvalde mass shooting:      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FWounded teacher condemns   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fpolice as cowards          
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A teacher wounded in a school shooting 
OL,6, in Uvalde, Texas, has criticised police
OL,7, as "cowards" for delaying taking action
OL,8, while his pupils were killed.          
OL,10,FIn a harrowing interview with ABC News 
OL,11,Fhe said he told his students to pretend
OL,12,Fto be asleep during the shooting.      
OL,14,FEleven of them died when the gunman    
OL,15,Fstalked his and an adjacent classroom  
OL,16,Ffor over an hour as police stood in the
OL,17,Fhall.                                  
OL,19,F"You had a bulletproof vest. I had     
OL,20,Fnothing," he said of the police.       
